1
00:00:06,600 --> 00:00:11,537
=The Moment I Met You=

2
00:00:11,537 --> 00:00:15,037
=Episode 20=

3
00:00:15,037 --> 00:00:18,000
(Prosperity For the Family)

4
00:00:18,519 --> 00:00:19,399
What's going on here?

5
00:00:20,879 --> 00:00:21,519
This...

6
00:00:23,199 --> 00:00:23,760
Since when

7
00:00:23,760 --> 00:00:25,320
was I promised to this guy?

8
00:00:27,160 --> 00:00:27,760
Chang,

9
00:00:28,760 --> 00:00:31,000
let us explain everything to you.

10
00:00:31,839 --> 00:00:33,079
You knew about this?

11
00:00:34,520 --> 00:00:38,679
Years ago, your grandfather
went to Xichuan on business.

12
00:00:39,399 --> 00:00:42,960
He happened to meet
Young Master Shen's father there.

13
00:00:43,920 --> 00:00:45,320
My father is...

14
00:00:45,320 --> 00:00:46,600
His father

15
00:00:46,759 --> 00:00:49,600
was a very prominent figure in Xichuan.

16
00:00:50,000 --> 00:00:51,880
He's the leader of the Xichuan outlaws.

17
00:00:52,439 --> 00:00:55,399
Your grandfather had
a drinking contest with Old Master Shen,

18
00:00:56,240 --> 00:00:58,640
and he lost.

19
00:00:58,880 --> 00:01:00,079
While he was still drunk,

20
00:01:00,079 --> 00:01:03,520
he went ahead
and signed this marriage contract.

21
00:01:03,880 --> 00:01:05,879
He sold his own granddaughter
over a few drinks?

22
00:01:05,879 --> 00:01:07,120
Has he never had wine before?

23
00:01:08,359 --> 00:01:10,159
We thought it was just a joke.

24
00:01:10,599 --> 00:01:12,959
We had no idea they'd take it seriously.

25
00:01:14,120 --> 00:01:16,519
Mrs. Mei, you might've seen it as a joke,

26
00:01:16,760 --> 00:01:18,480
but my family certainly didn't.

27
00:01:19,000 --> 00:01:22,319
I've come here
on my father's orders to marry her.

28
00:01:24,159 --> 00:01:25,079
Chang's never marrying

29
00:01:25,079 --> 00:01:26,239
someone like you.

30
00:01:27,439 --> 00:01:29,599
And who might
this impulsive young man be?

31
00:01:30,287 --> 00:01:31,528
I am quite young.

32
00:01:35,079 --> 00:01:36,159
He's my fiancé.

33
00:01:39,319 --> 00:01:40,400
You already have a fiancé?

34
00:01:40,599 --> 00:01:41,239
What of it?

35
00:01:41,599 --> 00:01:44,439
We're in love with each other,
and only with each other.

36
00:01:44,439 --> 00:01:45,200
None at all.

37
00:01:47,200 --> 00:01:49,084
Young Master Shen, look,

38
00:01:49,239 --> 00:01:52,079
it was all based on
a drunk wager back then.

39
00:01:52,079 --> 00:01:54,519
There's no need to take it so seriously.

40
00:01:55,000 --> 00:01:57,920
Chang already loves someone else.

41
00:01:58,760 --> 00:02:01,000
About this marriage contract...

42
00:02:01,840 --> 00:02:02,840
It is a serious matter

43
00:02:03,079 --> 00:02:05,120
determined by parents and matchmakers.

44
00:02:05,519 --> 00:02:06,879
I have the contract in my hand.

45
00:02:07,050 --> 00:02:08,159
She's marrying me,

46
00:02:08,439 --> 00:02:09,759
whether she wants to or not.

47
00:02:10,062 --> 00:02:12,680
Besides, if the Chu family
breaks their word,

48
00:02:12,680 --> 00:02:14,159
you will offend my people.

49
00:02:14,159 --> 00:02:15,560
Wait.

50
00:02:15,960 --> 00:02:16,800
Uncle!

51
00:02:17,439 --> 00:02:18,159
Chang,

52
00:02:18,560 --> 00:02:20,439
he does have the marriage contract.

53
00:02:21,039 --> 00:02:22,080
Maybe we should

54
00:02:22,080 --> 00:02:23,159
reconsider this.

55
00:02:23,159 --> 00:02:23,680
Exactly.

56
00:02:23,680 --> 00:02:24,560
Reconsider what?

57
00:02:25,125 --> 00:02:27,199
How about we reconsider
how to send him packing?

58
00:02:30,560 --> 00:02:32,639
It seems you need some time
to think this over.

59
00:02:33,000 --> 00:02:33,639
Very well.

60
00:02:34,080 --> 00:02:35,400
I shall give you three days.

61
00:02:36,120 --> 00:02:38,360
Whether we marry here in the Capital

62
00:02:38,360 --> 00:02:40,919
or back in Xichuan
makes no difference to me.

63
00:02:42,280 --> 00:02:43,879
My father is desperate for a grandson.

64
00:02:44,240 --> 00:02:45,879
He's losing his mind over it.

65
00:02:46,280 --> 00:02:46,840
You...

66
00:02:48,680 --> 00:02:49,360
Buyu.

67
00:02:53,825 --> 00:02:54,746
All right.

68
00:02:55,120 --> 00:02:55,919
Calm down.

69
00:02:56,000 --> 00:02:56,880
Let's have some tea.

70
00:02:58,240 --> 00:02:59,120
Chang.

71
00:03:08,240 --> 00:03:09,319
Shen Liefeng...

72
00:03:11,120 --> 00:03:12,000
Shen Liefeng!

73
00:03:12,439 --> 00:03:13,719
Eat my blade!

74
00:03:18,560 --> 00:03:19,719
What are you doing?

75
00:03:20,759 --> 00:03:22,240
Happiness was finally within my reach,

76
00:03:22,240 --> 00:03:23,520
and then this guy showed up.

77
00:03:23,520 --> 00:03:24,800
How can I not lose my temper?

78
00:03:26,600 --> 00:03:27,919
Do you really hate him that much?

79
00:03:28,240 --> 00:03:29,400
It isn't just hate.

80
00:03:29,960 --> 00:03:31,439
Looking at him makes me nauseous.

81
00:03:34,080 --> 00:03:34,879
But...

82
00:03:36,360 --> 00:03:38,360
I actually think he's quite handsome.

83
00:03:38,680 --> 00:03:40,000
What's handsome about him?

84
00:03:40,479 --> 00:03:41,319
He's so soft.

85
00:03:41,319 --> 00:03:42,520
Compared to Buyu,

86
00:03:42,759 --> 00:03:44,000
he's leagues behind.

87
00:03:44,000 --> 00:03:45,560
I still think he's good-looking.

88
00:03:47,520 --> 00:03:48,360
You like him?

89
00:03:49,240 --> 00:03:50,199
Then, you can marry him.

90
00:03:50,400 --> 00:03:51,400
I'll pay for your dowry.

91
00:03:51,400 --> 00:03:53,039
I'd be eternally grateful.

92
00:03:54,520 --> 00:03:56,319
Well, he isn't interested in me.

93
00:04:00,039 --> 00:04:01,400
Then, what should I do?

94
00:04:03,560 --> 00:04:05,639
You just want to
cancel the engagement, right?

95
00:04:06,120 --> 00:04:06,960
That's easy.

96
00:04:09,439 --> 00:04:10,479
What's your plan?

97
00:04:18,160 --> 00:04:19,120
What is it, Master?

98
00:04:20,079 --> 00:04:21,120
Did the proposal go wrong?

99
00:04:22,120 --> 00:04:23,079
Did they say no?

100
00:04:24,399 --> 00:04:25,920
Does that mean I still have a chance?

101
00:04:26,399 --> 00:04:28,040
Chang's fiancé has arrived.

102
00:04:30,560 --> 00:04:32,920
What? Another rival?

103
00:04:34,519 --> 00:04:36,199
Who is this guy anyway?

104
00:04:36,199 --> 00:04:37,160
Is he rich?

105
00:04:37,279 --> 00:04:38,519
How can he even compete with us?

106
00:04:39,199 --> 00:04:42,199
He has a marriage contract
signed by her grandfather.

107
00:04:42,480 --> 00:04:43,519
That's how.

108
00:04:47,160 --> 00:04:48,100
Wait, that's not right.

109
00:04:48,639 --> 00:04:50,240
If Yunchang is already betrothed,

110
00:04:50,439 --> 00:04:52,000
why is she discussing marriage with you?

111
00:04:52,380 --> 00:04:53,199
I don't believe it.

112
00:04:53,199 --> 00:04:54,240
That's not who she is.

113
00:04:54,920 --> 00:04:56,720
It was just a ridiculous mistake

114
00:04:57,000 --> 00:04:59,120
by those two old men after a few drinks.

115
00:05:00,639 --> 00:05:02,399
I see. You gave me a scare.

116
00:05:02,500 --> 00:05:03,959
Then, what are you still doing here?

117
00:05:03,959 --> 00:05:05,439
Why aren't you by Yunchang's side?

118
00:05:06,380 --> 00:05:07,439
Don't you have work to do?

119
00:05:07,759 --> 00:05:08,800
Stop pestering me.

120
00:05:10,160 --> 00:05:11,680
With that dull personality of yours,

121
00:05:11,680 --> 00:05:13,560
what does Yunchang even see in you?

122
00:05:14,000 --> 00:05:15,360
What are you so angry about?

123
00:05:15,360 --> 00:05:17,000
The other guy should be worried instead.

124
00:05:20,480 --> 00:05:21,920
By storming off like this,

125
00:05:21,920 --> 00:05:22,800
aren't you giving him

126
00:05:22,800 --> 00:05:24,079
the perfect chance to swoop in?

127
00:05:26,279 --> 00:05:27,000
I see.

128
00:05:27,580 --> 00:05:29,720
Why shouldn't I go spend time
with Yunchang right now?

129
00:05:29,750 --> 00:05:31,199
Maybe she will have a change of heart

130
00:05:31,199 --> 00:05:32,240
and fall for me instead!

131
00:05:32,240 --> 00:05:33,040
I'm going now.

132
00:05:34,000 --> 00:05:34,639
Come back here!

133
00:05:36,120 --> 00:05:36,959
What do you want?

134
00:05:37,500 --> 00:05:38,639
I'll buy you a drink later.

135
00:05:39,275 --> 00:05:40,439
Wait, what?

136
00:05:40,519 --> 00:05:41,240
Wait a second!

137
00:05:43,360 --> 00:05:44,240
Darn you.

138
00:05:46,737 --> 00:05:48,670
A lifetime of wit,
ruined by a moment of folly.

139
00:05:49,360 --> 00:05:50,879
Who gives advice to their own rival?

140
00:06:03,879 --> 00:06:04,839
A bit harder.

141
00:06:05,240 --> 00:06:06,480
Yes, Ms. Chu.

142
00:06:07,199 --> 00:06:07,959
That's the spot.

143
00:06:14,480 --> 00:06:15,279
Ms. Chu.

144
00:06:15,920 --> 00:06:16,839
You asked to see me?

145
00:06:22,399 --> 00:06:23,279
Young Master Shen.

146
00:06:23,600 --> 00:06:24,240
You're here.

147
00:06:26,399 --> 00:06:27,040
Have a seat.

148
00:06:27,160 --> 00:06:28,959
Are you all right?

149
00:06:31,560 --> 00:06:32,959
There is no need to be so afraid.

150
00:06:33,480 --> 00:06:35,439
Didn't you say you liked me?

151
00:06:36,160 --> 00:06:36,759
Come here.

152
00:06:49,839 --> 00:06:52,040
You seem like a different person today.

153
00:06:53,040 --> 00:06:54,759
So, which version of me do you prefer?

154
00:06:55,959 --> 00:06:57,399
Come on, keep going.

155
00:06:57,800 --> 00:06:58,480
Yes.

156
00:07:02,079 --> 00:07:03,120
Young Master Shen,

157
00:07:03,360 --> 00:07:04,879
don't be so stiff.

158
00:07:05,519 --> 00:07:06,439
Have a drink.

159
00:07:07,319 --> 00:07:09,560
This young man is quite the looker.

160
00:07:09,560 --> 00:07:10,759
Stay away from me!

161
00:07:11,519 --> 00:07:13,120
Aren't we all on the same side?

162
00:07:13,120 --> 00:07:14,040
Hey, handsome.

163
00:07:14,040 --> 00:07:16,000
Would you like me
to feed you some watermelon?

164
00:07:16,160 --> 00:07:16,759
No.

165
00:07:17,600 --> 00:07:18,439
I'll do it myself.

166
00:07:20,240 --> 00:07:20,959
Ms. Chu.

167
00:07:21,387 --> 00:07:22,666
What are you doing?

168
00:07:23,000 --> 00:07:24,000
Nothing.

169
00:07:24,360 --> 00:07:25,800
Just have a drink with me.

170
00:07:26,450 --> 00:07:28,291
Buyu is always so proper.

171
00:07:28,360 --> 00:07:29,560
He is quite a bore.

172
00:07:30,720 --> 00:07:32,680
Since we're the same kind of people,

173
00:07:32,959 --> 00:07:34,399
there's no need to pretend.

174
00:07:34,600 --> 00:07:36,759
Let's just enjoy the moment!

175
00:07:42,319 --> 00:07:44,839
You're being incredibly improper.

176
00:07:50,000 --> 00:07:51,199
I just love to eat,

177
00:07:51,199 --> 00:07:52,240
and I love handsome men.

178
00:07:52,240 --> 00:07:53,079
I also love...

179
00:07:59,199 --> 00:08:00,480
You're hardly a woman at all.

180
00:08:01,240 --> 00:08:01,920
What?

181
00:08:03,199 --> 00:08:04,759
Should a woman be virtuous and refined?

182
00:08:05,120 --> 00:08:06,360
Must she be good at doing chores

183
00:08:06,360 --> 00:08:07,279
and socializing?

184
00:08:18,199 --> 00:08:21,000
Actually, your free-spirited nature

185
00:08:21,279 --> 00:08:22,160
is quite refreshing.

186
00:08:22,160 --> 00:08:24,720
It suits the unconventional life
of the Martial World.

187
00:08:28,319 --> 00:08:30,680
I like it very much.

188
00:08:32,960 --> 00:08:34,039
Are you serious?

189
00:08:34,799 --> 00:08:37,080
You're a total creep!

190
00:08:45,039 --> 00:08:46,679
Fine, tell me.

191
00:08:47,262 --> 00:08:48,461
What kind of woman do you hate?

192
00:08:49,487 --> 00:08:51,807
I hate every woman in the world
except for you.

193
00:08:53,325 --> 00:08:55,039
You're really set on me, aren't you?

194
00:08:56,287 --> 00:08:57,360
Ms. Yunchang,

195
00:08:57,720 --> 00:08:58,799
what makes you say that?

196
00:08:59,587 --> 00:09:00,347
Fine.

197
00:09:00,712 --> 00:09:01,753
You're forcing my hand.

198
00:09:03,559 --> 00:09:05,360
You aren't planning to gather your Qi

199
00:09:05,360 --> 00:09:07,039
just to let out a loud fart, are you?

200
00:09:08,559 --> 00:09:09,159
You!

201
00:09:10,480 --> 00:09:12,519
I'll admit you startled me at first.

202
00:09:12,919 --> 00:09:14,799
But I did some digging before I arrived.

203
00:09:15,080 --> 00:09:16,559
You're not this kind of person at all.

204
00:09:17,039 --> 00:09:17,720
I know

205
00:09:17,840 --> 00:09:19,320
you're just trying to provoke me

206
00:09:19,320 --> 00:09:20,559
into hating you.

207
00:09:21,200 --> 00:09:22,200
After all this,

208
00:09:22,200 --> 00:09:23,320
surely you can tell

209
00:09:23,559 --> 00:09:24,759
that I don't like you?

210
00:09:26,320 --> 00:09:27,600
Well, I don't like you either.

211
00:09:29,960 --> 00:09:31,519
Then, why do you insist on marrying me?

212
00:09:33,679 --> 00:09:34,639
What's wrong with you?

213
00:09:35,600 --> 00:09:36,159
I...

214
00:09:37,879 --> 00:09:39,039
I must marry you.

215
00:09:41,039 --> 00:09:42,080
Then, listen closely.

216
00:09:42,279 --> 00:09:43,360
I will never marry you!

217
00:09:44,200 --> 00:09:45,120
Arguing is pointless.

218
00:09:45,360 --> 00:09:47,679
In three days,
you're coming to Xichuan to wed.

219
00:09:50,987 --> 00:09:51,746
Shen Liefeng!

220
00:09:51,987 --> 00:09:53,266
I'm never marrying you.

221
00:09:53,825 --> 00:09:55,426
Keep dreaming!

222
00:09:57,360 --> 00:09:59,039
Uncle, I'm calling off the engagement!

223
00:10:04,080 --> 00:10:05,080
Why are you still here?

224
00:10:06,039 --> 00:10:07,679
I'm here to visit the seniors,

225
00:10:08,039 --> 00:10:09,799
but they seem to have stepped out.

226
00:10:10,810 --> 00:10:11,990
It's just as well that you're here.

227
00:10:12,300 --> 00:10:13,279
Hand over the contract.

228
00:10:13,799 --> 00:10:15,639
Otherwise, don't even think
about leaving.

229
00:10:19,120 --> 00:10:20,679
Two against one, is it?

230
00:10:21,159 --> 00:10:23,120
I don't need help to handle you.

231
00:10:24,080 --> 00:10:25,159
Buyu isn't around today.

232
00:10:25,840 --> 00:10:27,039
You're not getting away.

233
00:10:27,039 --> 00:10:29,039
Are you really trying
to murder your own fiancé?

234
00:10:29,279 --> 00:10:30,000
Hand it over!

235
00:10:53,700 --> 00:10:54,440
Buyu!

236
00:10:54,562 --> 00:10:55,879
He's bullying me!

237
00:10:57,440 --> 00:10:58,399
Don't be ridiculous.

238
00:11:00,039 --> 00:11:00,679
Chang.

239
00:11:00,679 --> 00:11:02,639
Look! He has a blade!

240
00:11:05,700 --> 00:11:06,460
Shen Liefeng,

241
00:11:06,799 --> 00:11:07,679
since you're here,

242
00:11:07,960 --> 00:11:09,360
let's head inside for a chat.

243
00:11:12,800 --> 00:11:13,875
Fine by me.

244
00:11:22,679 --> 00:11:23,480
Shen Liefeng,

245
00:11:24,039 --> 00:11:25,159
Chang and I are here

246
00:11:25,159 --> 00:11:26,279
to make it clear to you.

247
00:11:26,737 --> 00:11:28,938
We are in love,

248
00:11:29,279 --> 00:11:30,799
and no one is going to separate us.

249
00:11:31,462 --> 00:11:33,399
(Honor in the Martial World)
I suggest you hand over that contract

250
00:11:33,587 --> 00:11:34,628
and return to Xichuan.

251
00:11:36,919 --> 00:11:37,919
Did you hear him?

252
00:11:39,080 --> 00:11:39,879
Mao,

253
00:11:40,279 --> 00:11:41,159
what makes you think

254
00:11:41,159 --> 00:11:42,720
you're worthy of marrying Ms. Chu?

255
00:11:43,020 --> 00:11:44,799
Do you even know
who Chu Yunchang really is?

256
00:11:44,799 --> 00:11:45,440
Shut up!

257
00:11:49,159 --> 00:11:49,759
Buyu,

258
00:11:49,759 --> 00:11:51,039
wait here for a moment.

259
00:11:51,799 --> 00:11:53,120
You, come with me.

260
00:12:00,039 --> 00:12:01,240
If you say another word,

261
00:12:01,320 --> 00:12:02,440
I'll have your life.

262
00:12:03,440 --> 00:12:05,879
He still doesn't know
you're the Sect Leader, does he?

263
00:12:05,879 --> 00:12:07,679
What do I have to say
for you to understand?

264
00:12:08,720 --> 00:12:11,039
That contract was nothing
more than a drunken mistake

265
00:12:11,039 --> 00:12:12,799
made by my unreliable grandfather.

266
00:12:12,799 --> 00:12:15,559
But the Shen family
values this alliance very highly.

267
00:12:17,320 --> 00:12:18,159
Haven't you heard?

268
00:12:18,159 --> 00:12:19,159
Forced love isn't sweet.

269
00:12:19,519 --> 00:12:21,080
It might not be sweet,

270
00:12:21,600 --> 00:12:23,279
but it still quenches the thirst.

271
00:12:24,279 --> 00:12:25,720
Since you put it that way,

272
00:12:27,080 --> 00:12:28,720
we settle this the Martial World's way.

273
00:12:29,120 --> 00:12:31,320
Are you two willing to have

274
00:12:31,679 --> 00:12:32,320
a duel for me?

275
00:12:33,000 --> 00:12:33,679
A duel?

276
00:12:36,840 --> 00:12:37,519
Fine.

277
00:12:38,325 --> 00:12:40,764
If he can best me
in the art of thievery,

278
00:12:41,050 --> 00:12:43,720
it'll prove he's worthy of marrying
a paragon of the martial world,

279
00:12:43,720 --> 00:12:45,080
the leader of the Sacred Hand Sect.

280
00:12:45,812 --> 00:12:47,292
But if he can't beat me,

281
00:12:48,080 --> 00:12:49,360
how is he worthy of marrying you?

282
00:12:50,440 --> 00:12:51,360
A thievery contest?

283
00:12:56,150 --> 00:12:58,759
(Honor in the Martial World)

284
00:12:58,759 --> 00:12:59,440
Constable Mao,

285
00:13:01,600 --> 00:13:02,240
have some tea.

286
00:13:05,360 --> 00:13:07,399
What do you think
they're discussing in there?

287
00:13:08,000 --> 00:13:09,000
Don't you worry.

288
00:13:09,080 --> 00:13:10,480
None of us likes that man.

289
00:13:10,799 --> 00:13:11,759
I'm sure whatever

290
00:13:11,759 --> 00:13:13,440
they're saying isn't exactly pleasant.

291
00:13:16,519 --> 00:13:17,480
That's not fair.

292
00:13:17,690 --> 00:13:18,440
A thievery contest?

293
00:13:18,440 --> 00:13:19,240
You're the Bandit Prince.

294
00:13:19,240 --> 00:13:19,960
Buyu is...

295
00:13:19,960 --> 00:13:20,850
With the Gate Bureau?

296
00:13:21,759 --> 00:13:23,080
You knew that, yet you're asking?

297
00:13:23,080 --> 00:13:24,240
He'd likely arrest you

298
00:13:24,240 --> 00:13:25,159
while you're talking.

299
00:13:25,399 --> 00:13:27,240
And then, my true identity
would be exposed.

300
00:13:27,240 --> 00:13:29,240
I can compete with him
without revealing who I am.

301
00:13:29,720 --> 00:13:32,480
But you'd have the advantage
in a thievery match.

302
00:13:32,799 --> 00:13:34,360
He wants to marry the Grandmaster.

303
00:13:34,600 --> 00:13:36,679
Should we test his skill
to catch thieves instead?

304
00:13:37,320 --> 00:13:37,919
You...

305
00:13:38,120 --> 00:13:39,879
This is the only condition I'll accept.

306
00:13:41,679 --> 00:13:42,320
Fine.

307
00:13:42,879 --> 00:13:43,879
You have a deal.

308
00:13:44,279 --> 00:13:46,279
But if you lose,
you call off the engagement.

309
00:13:47,279 --> 00:13:47,919
One more thing.

310
00:13:48,080 --> 00:13:49,320
If you dare expose my identity,

311
00:13:49,320 --> 00:13:50,240
I will kill you.

312
00:13:52,000 --> 00:13:53,080
It's a deal.

313
00:13:57,639 --> 00:13:58,360
What?

314
00:13:59,240 --> 00:14:00,679
Aren't you willing to take up

315
00:14:01,080 --> 00:14:01,960
his challenge for me?

316
00:14:01,960 --> 00:14:02,600
Wait...

317
00:14:03,759 --> 00:14:05,399
Of course I'd duel for our love.

318
00:14:05,500 --> 00:14:07,559
I've heard of matches
in poetry, music, or chess...

319
00:14:07,879 --> 00:14:10,320
even contests of wealth and influence.

320
00:14:10,320 --> 00:14:13,080
But a thievery contest?
What kind of match is that?

321
00:14:13,437 --> 00:14:14,118
Chang,

322
00:14:14,519 --> 00:14:15,480
I'm a constable.

323
00:14:15,480 --> 00:14:16,580
I can't go around stealing.

324
00:14:20,000 --> 00:14:21,080
It isn't stealing.

325
00:14:21,320 --> 00:14:23,320
It's just taking back
the marriage contract.

326
00:14:23,720 --> 00:14:24,919
How is that not stealing?

327
00:14:26,000 --> 00:14:27,879
Chang, think of another way.

328
00:14:29,960 --> 00:14:31,759
Fine, I'll see
what else I can come up with.

329
00:14:34,399 --> 00:14:36,720
Men are all the same.
Just talk and no action.

330
00:14:36,960 --> 00:14:37,759
If you ask me,

331
00:14:38,080 --> 00:14:40,200
you don't really
love Ms. Chu all that much.

332
00:14:41,875 --> 00:14:44,360
Chang, for you,
I'll take up the challenge.

333
00:14:44,759 --> 00:14:46,320
As long as it's not something immoral,

334
00:14:47,320 --> 00:14:48,200
make your move.

335
00:14:49,639 --> 00:14:50,320
Very well.

336
00:15:04,480 --> 00:15:06,320
The rules of the match are simple.

337
00:15:07,120 --> 00:15:08,039
Last night,

338
00:15:08,320 --> 00:15:09,200
I hid the contract

339
00:15:09,200 --> 00:15:11,320
behind the plaque at Zhengyang Gate.

340
00:15:12,200 --> 00:15:13,840
We have a ten-day limit.

341
00:15:14,200 --> 00:15:16,200
Whoever can retrieve it

342
00:15:16,200 --> 00:15:18,440
in broad daylight without being spotted

343
00:15:18,559 --> 00:15:19,679
wins the contract.

344
00:15:20,159 --> 00:15:23,080
The loser must give up their claim.

345
00:15:23,799 --> 00:15:26,360
Retrieving the contract
at Zhengyang Gate in broad daylight?

346
00:15:27,080 --> 00:15:28,159
He's lost his mind.

347
00:15:33,160 --> 00:15:34,279
If this is too much for you,

348
00:15:34,279 --> 00:15:35,600
we can try to find another way.

349
00:15:36,519 --> 00:15:37,799
It isn't that.

350
00:15:37,799 --> 00:15:39,919
Taking back the contract isn't illegal.

351
00:15:40,480 --> 00:15:41,519
I'm just...

352
00:15:48,039 --> 00:15:48,919
Just what?

353
00:15:49,300 --> 00:15:51,279
You know my lightness skill
isn't exactly great.

354
00:15:51,480 --> 00:15:53,039
I can manage a wall, but this?

355
00:15:53,360 --> 00:15:55,240
In broad daylight with a crowd watching?

356
00:15:55,840 --> 00:15:57,039
And I'm a constable.

357
00:15:58,519 --> 00:16:00,759
Then, I'll just have to use this chance

358
00:16:00,860 --> 00:16:02,480
to put you through
some special training.

359
00:16:04,559 --> 00:16:05,639
Special training?

360
00:16:11,325 --> 00:16:14,600
♪Grudges and regrets
are like strong wine♪

361
00:16:14,638 --> 00:16:17,513
♪Drink it down and let it go♪

362
00:16:18,013 --> 00:16:23,731
♪An empty cup for our love and hate♪

363
00:16:24,913 --> 00:16:28,233
♪Tears blur a fate I can't control♪

364
00:16:28,363 --> 00:16:31,283
♪Let's drink until dawn♪

365
00:16:32,451 --> 00:16:37,691
♪Behind this mask, I'll never lie♪

366
00:16:38,913 --> 00:16:41,306
♪Every reunion feels like the first♪

367
00:16:41,306 --> 00:16:44,956
♪This hidden smile will never fade♪

368
00:16:45,025 --> 00:16:48,515
♪One heart, standing by your side♪

369
00:16:48,613 --> 00:16:51,588
♪To the ends of time♪

370
00:16:51,588 --> 00:16:54,963
♪The moon traces your face♪

371
00:16:55,150 --> 00:16:58,738
♪Draped in clouds, you fill my heart♪

372
00:16:58,738 --> 00:17:04,978
♪To find you
and keep our promise forever♪

373
00:17:05,313 --> 00:17:08,528
♪A silent prayer in my soul♪

374
00:17:08,813 --> 00:17:12,351
♪Carrying my vow beneath the moon♪

375
00:17:12,638 --> 00:17:15,663
♪Hoping we never drift apart again♪

376
00:17:15,663 --> 00:17:18,763
♪On our way to forever♪

377
00:17:18,763 --> 00:17:22,613
♪The moon traces your face♪

378
00:17:22,613 --> 00:17:25,973
♪Draped in clouds, you fill my heart♪

379
00:17:26,163 --> 00:17:32,123
♪To find you
and keep our promise forever♪

380
00:17:33,200 --> 00:17:42,840
♪Just to be with you♪
